{"tid":980581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！2018年中國城鎮登記失業率3.8% 為近幾年來的新低！","createTime":"2019-01-13T15:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T06:42:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"389431901c7daf3d0a95a03afff7cf90a21ead5c","tid":980581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒報道，2018全年中國新增就業總數為1,361萬，按年增加10萬。而截至去年底，全國的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>城鎮登記失業率是3.8%，為近幾年來的新低</strong></span>。中國人力資源和社會保障部部長張紀南表示，就業職位總體上是供大於求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n他表示，今年1月1日起，「三年百萬青年見習計劃」已啟動，就業見習補貼範圍擴展至16至24歲的失業青年。他又指，有關部門會加快研究企業降低社保費率的實施方案，加大失業保險費的返還力度和幅度；並提高創業貸款額度，個人的貸款額度由10萬元人民幣(下同)提到15萬元，小微企業由200萬元提高到300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n市場關注，中國經濟放緩及貿易戰等因素對就業市場的影響。據早前內地媒體報道，因為蘋果公司削減iPhone訂單，導致富士康等手機廠要減產裁員。員工亦無法像以往靠加班賺取更多收入，部分僅能領取二千多元人民幣的底薪；一些二線手機廠，如錘子科技、金立亦先後被傳因陷入財困而要裁員。另外，亦接連有外資廠商表示考慮把生產線遷出中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190113/bkn-20190113220013414-0113_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190113%2Fbkn-20190113220013414-0113_00842_001.html&d=6D76kMxAeH9CPMZPX3MPI%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f4eaee12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190113/bkn-20190113220013414-0113_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"23f56cc7bfd4472cfdb2f248ee784ea8a2af8d0b","tid":980581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a51f58c29948064cb08ab65700ae584e8355c8a","tid":980581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"trump又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724230993433487887649cc4c1682262836d2456","tid":980581,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"解決失業人口，就冇失業問題<br />\n<br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"4db878d4b47f036f42163201fbbc61106aa8564e","tid":980581,"uid":31186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"回鄉創業麻<br />\n日本都玩過啦 全民freelance  都無失業"},{"pid":"184cf16faadbf621fc7d76204c48c118a2500152","tid":980581,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"大驚小怪<br />\n打錯字啫 38%咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dc01b2b433154ddf3e4422583020a5f39107d1","tid":980581,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"創業  自顧  邊度有失業姐"},{"pid":"a373659854b6673109c3be583390f143f3221f3c","tid":980581,"uid":223741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Tx85OC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Tx85OC.png&h=cb663779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLH5oAh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLH5oAh.png&h=b16abe03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ui9SN1X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fui9SN1X.png&h=98af0d19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4E2XY8C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4E2XY8C.png&h=776ecb6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac45e6709aba336ad7f553133b506b59ed8dc7b9","tid":980581,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}